Purpose of This Document
This file collects supplementary materials that sit outside the primary LinkedIn posts and YouTube transcripts folders. It includes conference talk summaries, newsletter excerpts, published articles, technical assessment notes, and key quotes — all drawn directly from the 10 experts profiled in this research project.
Everything here is primary-source material, not secondary commentary. The goal is to support a real playbook on AI-powered SEO content production.

